	[build woe] For libs, grow ‘LIBS’ R2L, not ‘EXTRALIBS’ L2R.

	* configure.ac: Check for libmwsock, libws2_32, libuser32,
	libshell32 and libadvapi32 using simplified AC_CHECK_LIB calls,
	reordered to grow right-to-left.

