2011-02-12  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[boot int] Use ‘AC_C_BIGENDIAN’.

	* configure.ac (svz_cv_sys_bigendian): Delete var.
	(WORDS_BIGENDIAN): Delete conditional AC_DEFINE.
	(AC_C_BIGENDIAN): New macro call.

