	* config.h.serveez: Delete file.
	* version.h.serveez: Likewise.
	* Makefile.am (config.h.serveez, version.h.serveez): New targets.
	(no-woe32): Also delete all *.serveez files in build tree.
	* .gitignore: Ignore all *.serveez files.

