	[build] Centralize Makefile.am var ‘MAINTAINERCLEANFILES’.

	* build-aux/common.mk (MAINTAINERCLEANFILES): New var.
	* Makefile.am (MAINTAINERCLEANFILES): Use ‘+=’; update.

